sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant Device

    Note over User,System,Device: Start of Bin Management Workflow

    rect rgb(210, 245, 255)
    Note over User,System: Add Bin Workflow
    User->>System: Click "Add Bin"
    System->>User: Show Add Bin Modal
    User->>System: Submit Bin Details
    System->>System: Validate and Process Add
    System->>User: Confirm Bin Added and Refresh List
    end

    rect rgb(245, 210, 210)
    Note over User,System: Edit Bin Workflow
    User->>System: Select Bin to Edit
    System->>User: Show Edit Bin Modal with Current Details
    User->>System: Modify and Submit Changes
    System->>System: Validate and Update Bin Data
    System->>User: Confirm Bin Updated and Refresh List
    end

    rect rgb(210, 255, 210)
    Note over Device,System: Bin Monitoring Workflow
    Device->>System: Send Sensor Data
    System->>System: Process Sensor Data and Update Status
    System->>User: Push Updates and Alerts (Full Bin Notifications)
    end

    Note over User,System,Device: End of Bin Management Workflow
